Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要逃学…去远方的什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为被看见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:00:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没什么好放在心上的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因为悠你准备时故意磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长她眼睛通红诶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么想肯定都有些内情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日野君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心吧  那件事我不会告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…我觉得那样做很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一个人  这么做太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直喜欢春日野君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为你是个温柔  认真又出色的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不会和你说话了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隐隐约约有些猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我希望是自己猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们…一直以来都是分开的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阔别许久回到我身边的穹  已经不是我所认识的妹妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了我从没见过的  一个纤弱柔美的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我真的…心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生过许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每每都会让我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那家伙很不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也因此  被她所依靠的时候更加让我怦然心动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.56,0:03:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想去守护她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她是我妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她是我妹妹…不能跨出那一步…我总是这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是在两年后的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有了一段别的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想把它变成一段真正的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总是不太顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我却依然想把它硬撑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果伤害了奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是不太顺利呢  真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:04:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一个人  这么做太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我希望是自己猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭做好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠？你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实一点都没有改变呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你怎么糟蹋我的身体都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要悠你想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…不是这样的  不是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是结束吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是接吻…还是更亲昵的举动…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:06:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是兄妹啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在说这些？为什么是兄妹就不能接吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不许性爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那个…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为不会被别人接受？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情我一点都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和悠在一起就好！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道还有其它很多问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但全部都无所谓！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么  就算是悠的小孩我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实没你想得那么简单！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把那些烦人的现实放到一边…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说得那么轻松…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说那些话？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经讨厌我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔发来短信了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:29.11,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我和真里子都在考虑让你们能\N过上安心的生活。只要你们方便\N的话，两个人分别住到我和真里\N子这边来怎么样。我和真里子一\N直都承蒙大哥照顾，所以我想我\N们也有将你们抚养成人的义务。\N具体等我回国之后直接见面谈吧。\N你和穹两个人都好好考虑一下。）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔他们要回日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和旭川阿姨已经谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经被发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们其实没多少储蓄…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢  这又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说他们一个人可以收养我们中的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么  难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们分开吧  这样才会更幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹  穹你在睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:23.48,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我虽然是悠的妹妹\N却想和悠接吻…\N想和悠连结在一起…\N但是这好像给悠添麻烦了呢…\N对不起…）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹她…她不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少可以确定  她应该没有乘电车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她可能去别人家了  但哪里都没有人影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他还有哪些有可能的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的活动范围应该不会很大…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在音乐教室里我没和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹她和我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这样就扯平了」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个夏天  小穹她好像看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹她是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你还想和她分开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说正因为如此  你才要和她分开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在寻找答案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去亮平家什么的看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢你  奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去我家后面的湖从头开始吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位于我们叉依姬神社内社的湖泊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说是万物起源
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比淤能碁吕岛更早存在  乃人类诞生之地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要去那儿的话人就可以转世重生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生就能从头开始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  穹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  穹  没能救你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  也许这是最好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让两人一同前往只有两个人的遥远世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为再也不会睁开眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹  已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:16:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕  对于两人的前途
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟会有什么等待着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我依然不知道该如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  两个人一起寻找好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找能好好珍惜这份心意的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不计较他人怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不在意自己会多痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想找到最能让穹得到幸福的路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湿成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖和吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你  穹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得这些成员凑在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉挺怀念的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也感觉是他们把我们凑到了一块
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有发短信过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次之后音讯全无
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚离开机场准备坐巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再换乘几次当地的长途汽车和地区短线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概三天后到达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到受过父母照顾的一个家具商的镇上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是天方夜谭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身两人去外国居住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂  这样真的能幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  对小悠来说  真正的挑战还在后头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就我而言  却不能断言小悠是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  爱上一个人的感情是无法抑止的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望他们能得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光有感情就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感情就能为所欲为的话  我也有很多想做的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沾到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎饼干  在嘴边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦掉没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦掉了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//--------------------M---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从伊福部小姐那里知道了来龙去脉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也问过家里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:21:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我必须得来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:01.75,title3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,305)}初佳与悠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.29,0:22:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初佳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我比你小又不可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没工作也挣不了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业后我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.13,0:22:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请永远留在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.11,0:22:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于明白了来这里的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了  我停止的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.07,0:22:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.43,0:22:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初佳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出洋相了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.13,0:22:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是初佳的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.02,0:22:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:22:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.38,0:23:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最终话了  我想不留遗憾地干一回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.47,0:23:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我换上这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不…我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.58,0:23:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人  今晚的初佳会对主人千依百顺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用千依百顺的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.13,0:23:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害羞  比如这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠  眼镜娘PLAY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.33,0:23:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是巫女PLAY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.35,0:23:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了  这是班长PLAY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦  在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.15,0:23:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢的是平常的初佳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.53,0:23:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的总结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.04,0:24:02.96,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1600,0)\pos(240,360)}悠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:24:02.96,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1600,0)\pos(340,360)}最最最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.88,0:24:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的最终话


